[MFLOG|0|2026-03-16T00:32:16.316322Z|runtime|a23051ce-93f1-4ba7-a9e2-8e77c95fe5f8]Using a slow image processor as `use_fast` is unset and a slow processor was saved with this model. `use_fast=True` will be the default behavior in v4.52, even if the model was saved with a slow processor. This will result in minor differences in outputs. You'll still be able to use a slow processor with `use_fast=False`.
